# Team 2: Explorer — Platform Story
# Lead: Ambassador | v0.18.3 | 27 March 2026
#
# CENTER OF GRAVITY (defined by Ambassador):
# "SG/Send is the gateway, not the destination. The website must hint at the
#  platform without overpromising. SGit is live — say so. SG-Vault is coming —
#  one line. The platform stack diagram is our most powerful investment signal
#  hidden in plain sight. Every visitor who 'gets it' becomes a champion."
#
# TEAM COMPOSITION
# Role         | Scope
# Ambassador   | Leads — platform narrative, positioning, launch content
# Sherpa       | Platform page copy, ecosystem section copy, SGit one-liner
# Designer     | Platform stack visual, ecosystem nav treatment
# Architect    | Cross-product architecture accuracy, claim verification
# Developer    | "Where we're going" section build, ecosystem nav
#
# WORKING FILES: .issues/website-redesign/explorer-platform/
#   platform-story.issues
#   ecosystem-navigation.issues
#   demo-content.issues
#
# KEY DOCS
