#   SG-Vault:      Section 3 of vision doc (browser UI for SGit vaults)
#   Demo content:  Section 13 of vision doc (SGraph infographics as demo files)
#
# CONSTRAINT: Only claim what's shipped.
#   SG/Send v0.3.0 → LIVE
#   SGit-AI       → LIVE (pip install sgit-ai, full CLI, own GitHub org)
#   SG-Vault      → "coming" (architecture exists, browser UI not yet shipped)
